{"tid":561264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（狗年報喜）董朝太監「路祥安」病逝！","createTime":"2018-02-15T00:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T07:54:51.000Z","uid":29314,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ef23481476e069e847723f46fded4535e13703a4","tid":561264,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:42:16.000Z","msg":"(星島日報報道) 本報獲悉，在董建華年代出任特首辦高級特別助理、現任香港中華能源基金會副秘書長的路祥安，本周一就疑因感染流感入住瑪麗醫院，短短兩日間病情急劇轉差病逝。<br />\n<br />\n路祥安病逝消息，昨天早上在政圈傳出。有熟悉路祥安的政圈人士表示，路本周一曾向友人表示患上流感，感到骨痛及肚瀉，同日他更急症入住瑪麗醫院。<br />\n<br />\n但短短兩日間病情急速惡化並病逝。據悉，路祥安過去生活一直健康，平日有行山、遛狗等習慣，友人對於他突然急病去世都甚感可惜難過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現年六十六歲的路祥安，本來是東方海外的高層員工，董建華九七年出任首任特首後，路祥安跟隨董建華加入政府，出任特首辦高級特別助理。<br />\n<br />\n二〇〇〇年，路祥安捲入「港大民調風波」，當年港大民意研究計畫主任鍾庭耀在報章撰文，指控董建華透過「中間人」向他施壓，要求停止進行有關特首及政府的民調，路祥安被指是施壓者，港大並成立獨立調查小組調查事件，但獲董建華力撐留任，至〇一年底才辭官。<br />\n<br />\n二〇一〇年，中華能源基金委員會於香港註冊成立，路祥安出任基金會副秘書長。基金會常務副主席何志平近期被美國政府指控行賄及洗黑錢，在美國被捕拘押。"},{"pid":"413665722c78b0fbfe069defe9522cf7120ca574","tid":561264,"uid":29314,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:44:21.000Z","msg":"何志平被捕，路祥安瓜左。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時到董建華？"},{"pid":"c566d01474e79b442baf0cadf89f273c5013f9be","tid":561264,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:46:57.000Z","msg":"狗年喜事一籮籮！<br />\n<br />\n要有請小鳳姐！"},{"pid":"0c8cce5fb8ef4cb1a9f3155013d92dbe5e85dca5","tid":561264,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"413665722c78b0fbfe069defe9522cf7120ca574","tid":561264,"uid":29314,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:44:21.000Z","msg":"何志平被捕，路祥安瓜左。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時到董建華？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:47:06.000Z","msg":"期待中"},{"pid":"1c0174ac5e85031d09024c9c8e78291d5e9b41f9","tid":561264,"uid":57376,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"差一日都過唔到年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a8d6502401d38229ed097cd8d62a6ba001a5f2","tid":561264,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:51:16.000Z","msg":"蝦兵蟹將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cc68f69e9b9fd2e54c26166eaf42ee4709e861","tid":561264,"uid":29314,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/02/20180215_PO_LU_02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F02%2F20180215_PO_LU_02.png&h=2d900ff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/blogger/2018/02/20180215_PO_LU_03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fblogger%2F2018%2F02%2F20180215_PO_LU_03.png&h=28f67e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有路祥安的朋友原本約了他周二見面，但周一收到他兩段whatsapp留言，路祥安在第一段留言話：「過去兩晚真的難忘，是痛得難忘。先是感冒，令我全身凍得發抖，好像虐疾，並引發肚瀉。繼而痛風突然發作，痛得難以入睡。我痛風已多年無發作，今次殺我一個措手不及，而且異常厲害，狗年不利我，信焉。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路祥安接著發第二個whatsapp短訊：「我現在舉步維艱，抱歉明天未能赴會了。」他的朋友想不到，這就是和路祥安最後的聯系。從whatsapp上看，路祥安最後上線時間是周二下午1:33分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/blogger/2018/02/20180215_PO_LU_05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fblogger%2F2018%2F02%2F20180215_PO_LU_05.png&h=ee997795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他的朋友話，路祥安說「狗年不利我」，他們之前也有談論過此話題，因為路祥安屬龍，立春後進入狗年，路祥安犯太歲，而他的年齡更是犯到正那一種。當時談論這些話題只是茶餘飯後的談話，怎料卻一語成籤。"},{"pid":"61ff5471d1fa7e2865d63e2fd7a14becd90eb250","tid":561264,"uid":139720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:54:53.000Z","msg":"路公公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb374727c45b47f67be16a2f1b5e60db735b194","tid":561264,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T00:59:55.000Z","msg":"一語成籤<br />\n<br />\n而家d報紙佬真係on9架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a6029f25b79d82e1ea491d762c7e9528a36948","tid":561264,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一語成籤<br />\n<br />\n而家d報紙佬真係on9架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記者人工低，自然質地差架啦。將就下啦"},{"pid":"923a2222977dc8330376e7d67184426d59ab15c0","tid":561264,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好開心"},{"pid":"1d6af02b932ce95f5b947e1715a97f5b9eb1ada4","tid":561264,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:14:34.000Z","msg":"都話啲流感針唔work啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27949723851c79d816a8ec2c92a02d0a2d46b07f","tid":561264,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d6af02b932ce95f5b947e1715a97f5b9eb1ada4","tid":561264,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:14:34.000Z","msg":"都話啲流感針唔work啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:16:14.000Z","msg":"佢有冇打呀??? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5575480ff42c35bd0bc609c040eff644c5d17482","tid":561264,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43a6029f25b79d82e1ea491d762c7e9528a36948","tid":561264,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一語成籤<br />\n<br />\n而家d報紙佬真係on9架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記者人工低，自然質地差架啦。將就下啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20171121/_2017112111040693552.jp